data.value:
This setup will upgrade your copy of Novetus to with New Clients, such as 2006S, 2007S, Graphicstoria Reskins, 2011E with a 2011M Leaderboard, and More! This is a unofficial overhaul mod that adds a ton of new items and clients to Novetus 1.1. This was not made by Bitl. Bitl does not own the copyright for ROBLOX Clients. Scripts were used to make functional clients. Open the readme.txt in The Novetus Folder for More Info
WARNING! THIS PACKAGE IS NOT COMPATIBLE WITH RBXLEGACY!
